products.title: Carnival 15 Ochre Roller Blind
products.metadescription: Carnival 15 ochre roller blind in yellow. Made to measure from 10.36 with free uk mainland delivery. This roller blind includes 5-year guarantee and child safety features.
products.productdescription:
Carnival roller blinds are great for kitchens, bathrooms or offices. A versatile fabric, carnival 15 fabrics are moisture-resistant, flame-retardant and anti-allergen coated, and is available in several fabulous, saturated colours. This sunshine yellow electric roller adds a bright splash of colour to your window, evoking feelings of positivity and warm summer days! 
 
At swiftdirectblinds, quality is important to us, so not only does this roller blind made by their expert team and comes with customer-first service, we also provide a five-year guarantee, for extra peace of mind!
 
 Product id: db-rbx1269 fabric colour: ochre material: 100% polyester headrail: durable aluminium roller tube supported by white steel brackets - top, face or side fix   control type: smooth continuous-looped chain energy saving rating: er2 - medium energy saving value - effective thermal retention light filtering: yes

products.title: Carnival 15 Lily Roller Blind
products.metadescription: Carnival 15 lily roller blind in green. Made to measure from 10.36 with free uk mainland delivery. This roller blind includes 5-year guarantee and child safety features.
products.productdescription:
Carnival 15, a beautiful plain fabric which comes in many powerful fresh colours, are a perfect addition to any room. 
 
This vibrant green roller blind will add a splash of colour to any room in your home.
